  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦The Legendary Journey of the Rolling Curtain General</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on the legendary journey of the Rolling Curtain General, collect fragments of the Glazed Lamp, challenge formidable foes, and build your own village. In this world where tradition and innovation intertwine, forge an unprecedented adventure in the realm of Journey to the West.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/7fa686a69ff27a120bdc314f103b2d1b.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/7fa686a69ff27a120bdc314f103b2d1b.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/7fa686a69ff27a120bdc314f103b2d1b.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦The Backstory of the Glazed Cup</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Rolling Curtain General, banished to the mortal realm for offending the Heavenly Court, must collect fragments of the Glazed Lamp to gradually restore his power and face the punishment from the heavens. The Glazed Lamp, a sacred artifact offered by the Dragon Clan to the gods, has its fragments scattered across the mortal world, transforming into demonic beings or merging into human society. Players will confront various demons, monsters, humans, and immortals, gather the fragments, and encounter iconic characters from Journey to the West, such as the Monkey King, Marshal Tianpeng, and Guanyin Bodhisattva, rekindling the past and present of the Journey to the West universe.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/f9815d1acfe26b797a0660a4e8f82172.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/f9815d1acfe26b797a0660a4e8f82172.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/f9815d1acfe26b797a0660a4e8f82172.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦Random Battles, New Challenges</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game offers four chapters, featuring over 20 boss battles and hundreds of weapons and magical treasures. Each battle presents a fresh challenge, and as the story progresses, players will unlock more combat styles and strategies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/dfc4b2f259ca70ebee15189dcd398c08.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/dfc4b2f259ca70ebee15189dcd398c08.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/dfc4b2f259ca70ebee15189dcd398c08.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦Traditional Chinese Art Style with Dynamic Levels</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each chapter includes one main map and two branching maps, with terrains covering mountains, underground palaces, rivers, and more. The terrain modules and monster combinations within the maps change randomly, showcasing the dynamic beauty of traditional Chinese art style.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/ef23a334b8e34fe04387e772542d75a4.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/ef23a334b8e34fe04387e772542d75a4.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/ef23a334b8e34fe04387e772542d75a4.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦Ink Wash and Shadow Puppetry Animated Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each character features hundreds of animated movements, thousands of hand-drawn images, and 3D-rendered 2D and Spine portrait animations, delivering smooth and detailed combat effects, and endowing each character with a unique fighting style and visual presentation.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/fc0e4c38b74b54892baf172f4339d5a9.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/fc0e4c38b74b54892baf172f4339d5a9.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/fc0e4c38b74b54892baf172f4339d5a9.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦Village Management and Tactical Sandbox</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In addition to combat, players can build and manage their own village. The game offers dozens of buildings with varied functions, including resource production facilities, defense towers, and living quarters.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/667fce71700e24655eb9a2a6bb4db9bb.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/667fce71700e24655eb9a2a6bb4db9bb.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/667fce71700e24655eb9a2a6bb4db9bb.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦The Legendary Journey of the Rolling Curtain General</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on the legendary journey of the Rolling Curtain General, collect fragments of the Glazed Lamp, challenge formidable foes, and build your own village. In this world where tradition and innovation intertwine, forge an unprecedented adventure in the realm of Journey to the West.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/7fa686a69ff27a120bdc314f103b2d1b.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/7fa686a69ff27a120bdc314f103b2d1b.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/7fa686a69ff27a120bdc314f103b2d1b.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦The Backstory of the Glazed Cup</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Rolling Curtain General, banished to the mortal realm for offending the Heavenly Court, must collect fragments of the Glazed Lamp to gradually restore his power and face the punishment from the heavens. The Glazed Lamp, a sacred artifact offered by the Dragon Clan to the gods, has its fragments scattered across the mortal world, transforming into demonic beings or merging into human society. Players will confront various demons, monsters, humans, and immortals, gather the fragments, and encounter iconic characters from Journey to the West, such as the Monkey King, Marshal Tianpeng, and Guanyin Bodhisattva, rekindling the past and present of the Journey to the West universe.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><s