, and more. The terrain modules and monster combinations within the maps change randomly, showcasing the dynamic beauty of traditional Chinese art style.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/ef23a334b8e34fe04387e772542d75a4.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/ef23a334b8e34fe04387e772542d75a4.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/ef23a334b8e34fe04387e772542d75a4.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦Ink Wash and Shadow Puppetry Animated Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each character features hundreds of animated movements, thousands of hand-drawn images, and 3D-rendered 2D and Spine portrait animations, delivering smooth and detailed combat effects, and endowing each character with a unique fighting style and visual presentation.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/fc0e4c38b74b54892baf172f4339d5a9.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/fc0e4c38b74b54892baf172f4339d5a9.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/fc0e4c38b74b54892baf172f4339d5a9.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✦Village Management and Tactical Sandbox</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In addition to combat, players can build and manage their own village. The game offers dozens of buildings with varied functions, including resource production facilities, defense towers, and living quarters.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/667fce71700e24655eb9a2a6bb4db9bb.poster.avif?t=1755158894\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/667fce71700e24655eb9a2a6bb4db9bb.webm?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309510/extras/667fce71700e24655eb9a2a6bb4db9bb.mp4?t=1755158894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
